                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mt-4 text-justify">I integrate quantitative modeling, GIS, and bioinformatics to tackle challenges in plant pathology and environmental science, focusing on disease distribution, biosecurity, and climate change impacts. My work leverages advanced statistical methods and machine learning for predictive analytics and sustainable agriculture.</p>
