                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mt-4 text-justify">As a Specialist Adviser at New Zealand’s Ministry for Primary Industries, I lead biosecurity and spatial intelligence projects, applying GIS, data modeling, and plant pathology to safeguard agricultural and environmental health.</p>
